{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通过比较不同物质的吸热能力，知道不同物质的比热容一</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">般</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不同</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">不同物质比热容一般不同。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">质量相等</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">水和</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">食用油、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相同规格</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">个酒精灯</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">质量相同的水和油</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">温度传感器、火柴</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.点燃酒精灯给烧杯加热；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.点击表单中的</span>&ldquo;开始记录&rdquo;按钮<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.观察图线的变化规律，得出结论。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相等质量的水和食用油，吸收</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">相同的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">热量</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，升高温度不同</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">水的比热容较大，可以用来做发动机冷却剂或暖气的介质。</span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}